name: Snapshots of the Planar
description:
"Snapshots of the Planar" is an eternal, generative audio piece. It is completely synthesized in the viewer's browser, in realtime.

Using carefully calibrated "Planar Technology", the synthesizer continuously modifies its timbre and behavior to provide 6-stages of primitive tranquility. The "Planar" rarely repeats, and instead eternally unfolds.

This piece marks the first in a series of exploratory OBJKTs built with Zequencer, a new tool for web-based music creation.

To listen: Press anywhere on the OBJKT. If on mobile, make sure to turn off "silent-mode".

To play with the underlying projkt, go here:
https://zequencer.io/create/QmTaMvjM2XRxzpbtX8XPUzDsqq8x9mK2gkmGa8gUDNM6XB
